{"tid":585191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"採野菇回家水煮　男子吃後中毒肝功能異常","createTime":"2018-03-08T12:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T12:16:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0c647743458a97b6b6d9c425229c2a79f0e40a61","tid":585191,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180308/s00001/3540bbcf9ead6a95a2e89cfc021184ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180308%2Fs00001%2F3540bbcf9ead6a95a2e89cfc021184ad.jpg&h=3bb67e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名57歲男子前日（6日）在大埔沙羅洞郊野，採摘一堆野生菇類，回家水煮後進食10多隻。他在大約19小時後出現上腹痛、嘔吐和腹瀉等病徵，昨晚到雅麗氏何妙齡那打素醫院急症室求診，今日入院。診斷證實其肝功能異常，目前情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n衛生防護中心表示，菇類引起食物中毒一般屬急性，病因包括進食後短時間內出現噁心、嘔吐和腹痛等腸道徵狀；部分菇類亦可能令人大量流汗、有幻覺、昏迷，更嚴重是其他神經系統病徵和肝衰竭，甚至死亡。<br />\n<br />\n中心續指，菇類難以辨別是否適宜食用，提醒市民切勿採摘野生菇類進食。若市民疑進食後中毒，應立即帶同剩餘菇菌求醫，以供辨識種類。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180308/s00001/1520507888246\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180308%2Fs00001%2F1520507888246&d=DbnstQSggiOfRAl7VhsQoIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=72786bdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180308%2Fs00001%2F1520507888246&h=2fa468b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180308/s00001/1520507888246</a>"}]}